<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Consent to Login</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/index.css">
</head>
<body>
<main>
<section class="hero">
<p class="eyebrow">Authorization request</p>
<h1>Consent to login</h1>
<p class="lede"><strong>{{client_name}}</strong> wants to use this service for logins.</p>
</section>
<section class="panel" aria-labelledby="consent-title">
<h2 id="consent-title">Review request</h2>
{{#if requests_email}}
<p>As part of the login process, it is requesting your email address.</p>
<p>Do you consent to sharing your email address, as stored on {{idp_basename}}, with the site {{client_name}}?</p>
{{else}}
<p>Do you consent to continuing the login process using your account on {{idp_basename}}?</p>
{{/if}}
<p class="muted">You are currently signed in as <strong>{{identity_email}}</strong>.</p>
<form class="button-group" action="/authorize/consent" method="post">
<button type="submit" name="decision" value="approve">Yes, continue</button>
<button class="secondary" type="submit" name="decision" value="deny">No, cancel</button>
</form>
</section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
